---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="SocialProof vs Reviews.io — Which is Right for Small Business?" description="Comparing SocialProof and Reviews.io? See how pricing, setup complexity, and ownership of reviews differ. SocialProof starts free. Reviews.io starts at $89/month." canonical="https://socialproof.dev/vs/reviews-io">
<style>
    .hero { padding: 80px 24px 56px; text-align: center; max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: 2.6rem; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.15; color: #111; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .hero p { font-size: 1.2rem; color: #555; margin-bottom: 36px; }
    .cta-group { display: flex; gap: 14px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .summary-box { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto 40px; padding: 0 24px; }
    .summary-inner { background: #f4f0ff; border-radius: 12px; padding: 28px 32px; }
    .summary-inner h2 { font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .summary-inner p { font-size: 1rem; color: #444; line-height: 1.7; }
    .comparison-table { max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 24px; }
    .comparison-table h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 32px; text-align: center; }
    table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
    th { background: #f4f4f4; padding: 14px 16px; text-align: left; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #555; font-weight: 600; }
    th:first-child { width: 38%; }
    td { padding: 14px 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; font-size: 0.95rem; color: #333; vertical-align: top; }
    .winner { background: #f0fdf4; font-weight: 600; color: #15803d; }
    .badge { display: inline-block; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 20px; margin-left: 6px; }
    .badge-green { background: #dcfce7; color: #166534; }
    .pros-cons { max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 24px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 32px; }
    .pros-cons h2 { font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .pros-cons ul { padding-left: 18px; color: #444; font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.9; }
    .card-green { background: #f0fdf4; border-radius: 12px; padding: 28px; }
    .card-yellow { background: #fffbeb; border-radius: 12px; padding: 28px; }
    .use-case { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 24px; }
    .use-case h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 28px; text-align: center; }
    .use-case-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 24px; }
    .uc-card { border-radius: 10px; padding: 24px; border: 1.5px solid #eee; }
    .uc-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .uc-card p { font-size: 0.92rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; }
    .highlight { border-color: #6c47ff; }
    .cta-section { background: #111; color: #fff; padding: 60px 24px; text-align: center; margin-top: 40px; }
    .cta-section h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .cta-section p { font-size: 1.1rem; color: #aaa; margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .btn-primary { background: #6c47ff; color: #fff; padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; }
    .btn-ghost { background: transparent; color: #fff; border: 1.5px solid #555; padding: 13px 28px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; }
    .btn-secondary { background: transparent; color: #111; border: 1.5px solid #ccc; padding: 13px 28px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; }
    nav { border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; padding: 16px 24px; }
    nav a { font-weight: 600; color: #111; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem; }
    .footer-links { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 24px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #eee; }
    .footer-links a { color: #6c47ff; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem; margin: 0 12px; }
    @media (max-width: 600px) { .pros-cons, .use-case-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
</style>

<nav><a href="/">← SocialProof</a></nav>

<section class="hero">
  <h1>SocialProof vs Reviews.io — honest comparison for small business</h1>
  <p>Reviews.io is a powerful platform built for enterprise review management. SocialProof is built for small businesses that want authentic testimonials on their website — without the $89/month starting price.</p>
  <div class="cta-group">
    <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn-primary">Try SocialProof free &rarr;</a>
    <a href="/#demo" class="btn-secondary">See a live demo</a>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="summary-box">
  <div class="summary-inner">
    <h2>TL;DR</h2>
    <p>Reviews.io is a full-stack review platform with integrations into Trustpilot, Google, and major ecommerce platforms. If you're a mid-market retailer managing thousands of product reviews across multiple channels, it's a serious tool. If you're a service business or solopreneur who just wants to collect a few authentic testimonials and put them on your website — it's 10x the price you need to pay and 10x the complexity.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="comparison-table">
  <h2>Feature comparison</h2>
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Feature</th>
        <th>SocialProof</th>
        <th>Reviews.io</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>Starting price</td>
        <td class="winner">Free forever (1 widget) / $9/mo Pro <span class="badge badge-green">Winner</span></td>
        <td>$89/month (Starter)</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Setup time</td>
        <td class="winner">Under 5 minutes — shareable link + 2-line embed <span class="badge badge-green">Winner</span></td>
        <td>30–60 minutes; platform integration setup required</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Target customer</td>
        <td class="winner">Solopreneurs, small service businesses, local shops <span class="badge badge-green">Our focus</span></td>
        <td>Mid-market ecommerce brands, 50+ employees</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Approval before publish</td>
        <td class="winner">Yes — every testimonial reviewed before display <span class="badge badge-green">Winner</span></td>
        <td>Moderation available on higher plans</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Website embed</td>
        <td class="winner">2-line snippet, works on any site builder</td>
        <td>Available — more configuration needed</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Ecommerce integrations</td>
        <td>Roadmap — Shopify widget in progress</td>
        <td class="winner">Deep Shopify, Magento, WooCommerce integration <span class="badge badge-green">Winner</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Syndication to Google/Trustpilot</td>
        <td>Not currently</td>
        <td class="winner">Yes — major differentiator for retailers <span class="badge badge-green">Winner</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Photo/video reviews</td>
        <td>Text testimonials + text quotes</td>
        <td class="winner">Full rich media support</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>You own the data</td>
        <td class="winner">Yes — export anytime</td>
        <td>Yes — export available</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Free plan</td>
        <td class="winner">Yes — free forever for 1 widget</td>
        <td>Trial only (no permanent free tier)</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

<section class="pros-cons">
  <div class="card-green">
    <h2>SocialProof: best for</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Service businesses: coaches, consultants, therapists</li>
      <li>Local businesses: restaurants, salons, studios</li>
      <li>Solopreneurs who want a simple trust widget</li>
      <li>Anyone who needs testimonials on their site in under an hour</li>
      <li>Startups and early-stage products on a tight budget</li>
      <li>Non-technical founders — no developer required</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="card-yellow">
    <h2>Reviews.io: best for</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Ecommerce brands with product review needs at scale</li>
      <li>Businesses running Google Shopping ads (syndication matters)</li>
      <li>Teams with a dedicated marketing manager</li>
      <li>Companies that need Trustpilot + Google + site all synced</li>
      <li>High-volume review management (100+ reviews/month)</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="use-case">
  <h2>Pick the right tool for your situation</h2>
  <div class="use-case-grid">
    <div class="uc-card highlight">
      <h3>You run a yoga studio and want 3 testimonials on your homepage</h3>
      <p><strong>Use SocialProof.</strong> Send a collection link to your best students. Approve the responses. Paste the embed code. Done in an afternoon. $0.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="uc-card">
      <h3>You run a 500 SKU Shopify store and need product reviews</h3>
      <p><strong>Reviews.io makes sense.</strong> You need verified purchase reviews, syndication to Google, and rich media. That's their wheelhouse.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="uc-card highlight">
      <h3>You're a freelance designer who wants testimonials on your portfolio</h3>
      <p><strong>Use SocialProof.</strong> It's free, takes 10 minutes to set up, and displays beautifully on any site.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="uc-card">
      <h3>You need star ratings to show up in Google Shopping results</h3>
      <p><strong>Reviews.io handles this.</strong> Seller ratings syndication to Google is a specific feature we don't offer yet.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-section">
  <h2>Not paying $89/month for testimonials.</h2>
  <p>SocialProof is free forever for one widget. Pro is $9/month. Set up in under 5 minutes.</p>
  <div style="display: flex; gap: 14px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
    <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn-primary">Start free &rarr;</a>
    <a href="/#demo" class="btn-ghost">See a live demo</a>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="footer-links">
  <a href="/vs/birdeye">vs Birdeye</a>
  <a href="/vs/trustpilot">vs Trustpilot</a>
  <a href="/vs/podium">vs Podium</a>
  <a href="/vs/senja">vs Senja</a>
  <a href="/vs/elfsight">vs Elfsight</a>
  <a href="/for/ecommerce">For Ecommerce</a>
  <a href="/for/shopify">For Shopify</a>
</div>

</Base>
